▌  exact                                    exact                                                                      ┃
                                                                                                                       ┃
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@  exact 01                                                                                                            ┃
│  exact 02                                                                                                            ┃
│  exact 03                                                                                                            ┃
│  exact 04                                                                                                            ┃
│  exact 05                                                                                                            │
│  exact 06                                                                                                            │
│  exact 07                                                                                                            │
```

This snapshot shows a preview that is one line taller than the viewport, so the
preview scrollbar should now be visible.

    :k C-u overflow down
    :snap

